Author: sintos-compa
Text: Classic “people won’t say a peep if you gain weight, but you lose a pound everyone suddenly becomes an expert in human nutrition”

Author: ijustneededaname
Text: Everyone wants to be able to fix visibly anorexic people and treat them like their personal pet project to make them feel better about themselves. It's gross how people see someone who's unwell and think they suddenly have the right, nay, the duty, to play boss 🙄
